SUMMARY:Strength Training at Hanna City Center
LOCATION:Hanna City Center 2555 E. Hanna Avenue Tampa \, FL United States
DESCRIPTION:REGISTER HERE (https:calendly.comcot-uhc-onsite-repsstrength-h
 anna-city-center) Employees must register in advance. 10-person minimum or
  class will be cancelled and each class is capped at 30 participants so pl
 ease register early. The address is: 2555 E. Hanna Avenue in Tampa\, 33610
  Please note: These classes are for City of Tampa employees only and you w
