DESCRIPTION:Get ready for an exciting celebration as the Annual Brazilian 
 Festival returns to Tampa for its 16th edition. Tampa\, nestled on Florida
 s Gulf Coast\, was named by Time Magazine as one of the Worlds Greatest Pl
 aces\, and The Best Place to Live according to Forbes. Since its inception
  in 2012\, the Annual Brazilian Festival (https:brazilianfestival.org) has
  become the most traditional community event in the State of Florida\, a b
 eacon and symbol of Brazils rich musical heritage and cultural diversity\,
  showcasing some of Brazils pioneering renowned artists\, promoting multic
 ultural unity\, to inspire environmental awareness. \n\nPermalink: https:/
 /www.tampa.gov/node/174851
