SUMMARY:Remix: The Etruscans
LOCATION:120 W Gasparilla Plaza Tampa FL Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Remix is a series of make-and-take art workshops for adults in
 spired by the Museums current exhibitions with a new project every month. 
 This months project will be inspired by our The Etruscans: A Mysterious It
 alian People (https:tampamuseum.orgthe-etruscans-a-mysterious-italian-peop
 le) exhibition. Paint and decorate your own personal box\, similar to the 
 detailed ash boxes of the Etruscans! Ages 18 Workshops are designed to be 
 enjoyed by participants of any skill level\, and all materials are provide
 d. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/177226
